      "name": "Build List Panel",
      "type": "dashboard_panel",
      "prompt": {
        "positive": "A sleek, minimalist dashboard panel showing a list of active and completed software builds. The panel should have a dark background, monospace font, and clear status indicators for each build. The layout should be clean and easy to scan, with key details like timestamps, duration, and build status prominently displayed.",
        "negative": "Avoid bright colors, animations, or any distracting visual elements. Do not include placeholder or mock data - the panel should display real build information."
